room_title: Escape room "The Elevator" by Glenwood Escape Room in Glenwood Springs
room_description:
High above wall street your elevator has come to a stop between floors.  An investor that has lost everything has placed a bomb on board.  Your only objective is to disarm the bomb before the clock runs out and your elevator plummets to the basement.

Do you have what it takes to beat the bomb!?
